T02TD3351E:35a-1: mee tri ya s'a dha nam /
T02TD3351E:35a-4: rgyal ba byams pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3351E:35a-5: sngon du bstan pa thams cad nyid byas te /
T02TD3351E:35a-6: 'on kyang mi gi yi ge yongs su rdzogs pa yi //
T02TD3351E:35a-7: thub pa skyes mchog byams pa ni //
T02TD3351E:35a-8: zhal gsum spyan gsum gyis brgyan pa //
T02TD3351E:35a-10: sems dpa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa //
T02TD3351E:35a-11: phyag bzhi dag gis rnam par mdzes //
T02TD3351E:35a-12: chos ston pa yi phyag rgya yis //
T02TD3351E:35a-13: phyag gnyis dag ni rnam par brgyan //
T02TD3351E:35a-14: g-yas pa'i phyag ni gnyis pa na //
T02TD3351E:35a-15: mchog sbyin sems can skyong ba'o //
T02TD3351E:35a-16: g-yon na lha rdzas yal ga ni //
T02TD3351E:35a-17: klu shing me tog bcas pa'o //
T02TD3351E:35a-18: sangs rgyas sprin ni rab spro zhing //
T02TD3351E:35a-19: byang chub sems dpa' de bzhin 'bar //
T02TD3351E:35a-20: zla ba'i gdan dang dkyil 'khor yang //
T02TD3351E:35a-21: dngos grub mgon po bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3351E:35a-22: de nas phyag rgya bcing byas la //
T02TD3351E:35a-23: mnyam par bzhag pas sngags bzlas bya //
T02TD3351E:35a-24: lag gnyis so so dag tu bya //
T02TD3351E:35a-25: khu tshur bcings te sdigs mdzub gnyis //
T02TD3351E:35a-26: mthe bo'i dbus su gzhag bya ste //
T02TD3351E:35a-27: me tog sna tshogs mchod par bya //
T02TD3351E:35a-29: aom meem mee tri ya sv'ah'a /
T02TD3351E:35a-30: byams pa'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3351E:35a-31: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3351E:35a-32: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o//
